Module it.polimi.ingsw
Package it.polimi.ingsw.Network.Client

Interface ClientListener

All Known Implementing Classes:
Cli, ClientManager, GuiMaster
public interface ClientListener
The ClientListener interface defines methods for handling responses received from the server. An implementation of this interface allows the client to receive and handle different types of messages sent by the server.
